Package: glycoTraitR
Type: Package
Title: Compute and analyze the glycan structrual traits from GPSM data.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person("Bingyuan", "Zhang",
             email = "zhang.bingyuan.w8@f.mail.nagoya-u.ac.jp",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4892-323X"))
    )
Maintainer: The package maintainer <zhang.bingyuan.w8@f.mail.nagoya-u.ac.jp>
Description: 
    Tools for parsing glycan structures, computing monosaccharide 
    composition and structural traits, and performing differential 
    analysis of glycan heterogeneity from glycopeptide-spectrum-match (GPSM) 
    results produced by the pGlyco3 or Glyco-Decipher search engines. 
    The package builds trait-by-PSM matrices stored in a SummarizedExperiment 
    object, supports user-defined structural motifs, and provides plotting 
    utilities for visualization and interpretation of glycan trait changes.
URL: https://github.com/matsui-lab/glycoTraitR
